source.name: Mortgage Fraud Suspicious Activity Report (SAR) Data by State
source.description: This dataset provides a geographic breakdown by state of subjects identified in suspicious activity report (SAR) filings on suspected mortgage fraud. Files contain metadata expanding on the derivation, use, and limitations of FinCEN Mortgage Fraud SAR data. The Excel files provide mortgage fraud SAR data from filings received by FinCEN from 2006 to the most recent data.
